---
/* -----------------------------------------------------------------------
   Chandler Business Broker — city local-SEO page (fidelity: "close enough").
   Faithful clone of https://www.philsellsbiz.com/chandler-business-broker/
   Markup/copy verbatim from reference/chandler-business-broker-raw.html.
   Section CSS lifted from the live used-CSS
   (reference/_css-chandler-business-broker.css → _chandler-section-css.txt).
   NOTE: this city page does NOT use the full banner/philo/vid template the
   way Mesa/Gilbert do — it uses a lighter bespoke layout (.hlpr-sect chrome,
   .cbi-info-block / .consultant-section / .features-grid grids + accordion).
   Sections in DOM order:
     1. title-bar         — H1 city headline band
     2. hlpr-sect intro   — H2 + intro-block (phil-portrait + 2 paras)
     3. test-sctn-alt     — reviews title + 6 Google reviews
     4. cbi-info-block    — "What Is A CBI?" 2-col (text + photo)
     5. directory-flex    — 8 directory listing badges
     6. consultant-section— H3 + para + (video + benefits-text)
     7. features-grid     — 6 feature cards (icon + heading + para)
     8. faq-sctn          — FAQ accordion (<details>, faq-main-col)
     9. lctn-sctn         — 5 neighborhood cards (grid-locations)
   ----------------------------------------------------------------------- */
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SITE_URL } from "../config/site";
import financialServiceSchema from "../../reference/home-financialservice-schema.json";
import reviewsSchema from "../../reference/city-chandler-reviews.json";

/* Live <title> + meta description, verbatim */
const pageTitle = "Chandler Business Broker | Phil Reese";
const pageDescription =
  "Are you looking to sell or buy a business in Chandler? Contact Chandler business broker Phil Reese today at (480) 428-8010!";

const ogImage = `${SITE_URL}/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/chandler-business-broker.jpg`;

/* Live emits a WebPage @graph + standalone FinancialService + Reviews (no FAQPage). */
const webPageSchema = {
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "@id": `${SITE_URL}/chandler-business-broker/`,
  url: `${SITE_URL}/chandler-business-broker/`,
  name: pageTitle,
  isPartOf: { "@id": `${SITE_URL}/#website` },
  primaryImageOfPage: { "@id": `${SITE_URL}/chandler-business-broker/#primaryimage` },
  image: { "@id": `${SITE_URL}/chandler-business-broker/#primaryimage` },
  thumbnailUrl: ogImage,
  datePublished: "2017-10-30T22:38:30+00:00",
  dateModified: "2026-06-12T20:53:43+00:00",
  description: pageDescription,
  breadcrumb: { "@id": `${SITE_URL}/chandler-business-broker/#breadcrumb` },
  inLanguage: "en-US",
  potentialAction: [{ "@type": "ReadAction", target: [`${SITE_URL}/chandler-business-broker/`] }],
};
const primaryImageSchema = {
  "@type": "ImageObject",
  inLanguage: "en-US",
  "@id": `${SITE_URL}/chandler-business-broker/#primaryimage`,
  url: ogImage,
  contentUrl: ogImage,
  width: 1200,
  height: 1200,
};
const breadcrumbSchema = {
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "@id": `${SITE_URL}/chandler-business-broker/#breadcrumb`,
  itemListElement: [
    { "@type": "ListItem", position: 1, name: "AZ Business Broker", item: `${SITE_URL}/` },
    { "@type": "ListItem", position: 2, name: "Chandler’s Leading Business Broker" },
  ],
};

const structuredData = [
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@graph": [webPageSchema, primaryImageSchema, breadcrumbSchema],
  },
  financialServiceSchema,
  reviewsSchema,
];

/* ---------- 6 Google reviews (test-sctn-alt), verbatim ---------- */
const reviews = [
  { body: "Phil is honest and trustworthy.  He quickly earned my trust with his professionalism, clear communication, and consistently excellent guidance.  He was instrumental in getting our deal done.  Highly recommend!", name: "Bobby Pierce", url: "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNmeF8yUXNnRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xd59527a5c7d15195!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICfx_2QsgE%7CCgwIstfYuwYQiMut5AI%7C?hl=en-US" },
  { body: "Would recommend Phil Reese in a heartbeat He gives his all in selling your business.  He listed ours and sold it within 2 months.  Everything went so so smooth and he took care of everything.  I give him 10 stars.", name: "Gary Campbell", url: "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURxeU4zSTZBRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xd59527a5c7d15195!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDqyN3I6AE%7CCgwIoJLfhgYQqPes0gM%7C?hl=en-US" },
  { body: "Phil came highly recommended to us after selling a friend of ours business. So we gave him a call and Phil did a great job selling our business. He was there every step of the way going out of his way to help in all areas. I would and will recommend him to anyone wanting to sell their business.", name: "Joanne Manning", url: "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR5OFktUVZnEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0xd59527a5c7d15195!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDy8Y-QVg%7CCgwIs8yoggYQsPS01AM%7C?hl=en-US" },
  { body: "Phil was exceptional throughout the entire process. We highly recommend him to help sell or buy a small business.", name: "Kale Huycke", url: "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURjaHNta1R3EAE!2m1!1s0x0:0xd59527a5c7d15195!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDchsmkTw%7CCgwIhcz59gUQ-I3y3AE%7C?hl=en-US" },
  { body: "Phil was very professional in facilitating our transaction.  He knew what he was doing and is quite competent in following through with documenting the transaction and keeping all parties to the deal on track.  I'd recommend him to anyone seeking a competent business broker.", name: "Doug L", url: "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR3M082MDJnRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xd59527a5c7d15195!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDw3O602gE%7CCgwI4cuJ3gUQ2KC98wI%7C?hl=en-US" },
  { body: "Trustworthy, professional and hardworking.", name: "Lacey Kilfoyl", url: "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUN3aGJqVVhBEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0xd59527a5c7d15195!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICwhbjUXA%7CCgwIpsjWzgUQwICyiQM%7C?hl=en-US" },
];

/* ---------- Directory listing badges (directory-flex), verbatim ---------- */
const dirBadges = [
  { img: "dir-manta.png", alt: "Chandler Business Broker On Manta", title: "Local Chandler Business Broker on Manta", href: "http://www.manta.com/c/mx61w9v/phil-reese-arizona-business-broker", w: 65, h: 67 },
  { img: "dir-ibegin.png", alt: "Chandler Business Broker on iBegin", title: "Local Chandler Business Broker on iBegin", href: "http://www.ibegin.com/directory/us/arizona/phoenix/phil-reese-arizona-business-broker-4505-e-chandler-blvd-170a-1/", w: 65, h: 67 },
  { img: "dir-crunchbase.png", alt: "Chandler Business Broker On CrunchBased", title: "Local Chandler Business Broker on Crunchbased", href: "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/phil-reese-arizona-business-broker", w: 65, h: 67 },
  { img: "dir-hotfrog.png", alt: "Expert Chandler Business Broker On Hotfrog", title: "Local Chandler Business Broker on Hotfrog", href: "https://www.hotfrog.com/company/1099478479065088/phil-reese-arizona-business-broker/scottsdale/business-financial-services", w: 65, h: 67 },
  { img: "dir-cylex.png", alt: "Chandler Business Broker On Cylex", title: "Local Chandler Business Broker on Cylex", href: "https://phoenix.cylex-usa.com/company/phil-reese--arizona-business-broker-25795631.html", w: 65, h: 67 },
  { img: "dir-spoke.png", alt: "Chandler Business Broker On Spoke", title: null, href: null, w: 65, h: 67 },
  { img: "dir-showmelocal.png", alt: "Chandler Business Broker On Show Me Local", title: "Local Chandler Business Broker on ShowMeLocal", href: "http://www.showmelocal.com/profile.aspx?bid=21790129", w: 65, h: 67 },
  { img: "dir-tuugo.png", alt: "Chandler Business Broker On Tuugo", title: "Local Chandler Business Broker on Tuugo.Us", href: "http://www.tuugo.us/Companies/phil-reese-arizona-business-broker4/0310006286664", w: 65, h: 67 },
];

/* ---------- 6 feature cards (features-grid), verbatim ---------- */
const features = [
  { img: "feat-which-broker.png", alt: "Find out which Chandler broker is right for you", title: "Which Chandler Broker is Right For Me?", body: "Phil Reese, designated CBI, can get you the best results on your business sale. He knows the Chandler business market, and can give your business the right amount of exposure that it needs.", w: 66, h: 66 },
  { img: "feat-sell-business.png", alt: "Get your business in Chandler sold with a business broker", title: "Sell Your Chandler Business With a Business Broker", body: "Experienced broker Phil Reese can help you sell your Chandler business with ease, and can get you the best possible price for your retail business with discreet, but extensive, market exposure.", w: 64, h: 64 },
  { img: "feat-expert.png", alt: "Get expert advice about your Chandler business from a business broker", title: "Expert Chandler Business Broker Advice", body: "Business broker Phil Reese has just the expert broker sale advice you need. Phil Reese has sold over 50 businesses, and continues to do help business sales with over 10 years of professional experience.", w: 64, h: 64 },
  { img: "feat-why-sell.png", alt: "Learn more about selling your service business in Chandler", title: "Why Sell a Chandler Business?", body: "If you feel you have a better opportunity, or you have personal reasons, you may want to sell your company. Selling your service business has never been easier, thanks to expert broker Phil Reese.", w: 64, h: 64 },
  { img: "feat-valuation.png", alt: "Learn more about business valuation by a Chandler business broker", title: "Chandler Business Broker Valuation Services", body: "Don’t try to sell alone; get help with valuating your company from a certified business broker. Phil Reese is an expert in business valuation, and can assure you the best possible price for your business.", w: 64, h: 64 },
  { img: "feat-local.png", alt: "Learn more about selling your local Chandler business", title: "Help With Selling Your Local Chandler Business", body: "Local businesses are known for being appeciated by the community that they’re in, but can be tough to sell. Luckily, help with selling in your local Chandler area is available, from CBI Phil Reese.", w: 64, h: 64 },
];

/* ---------- FAQ accordion (faq-sctn, faq-main-col), verbatim ----------
   `qLead` preserves the live spacing after "Q:" (first item has none). */
const faqs = [
  { qLead: "", q: "Which Documents Are Required To Sell Your Business?", a: "When you are ready to sell your business and move along to your next step, it is vital to have the appropriate document and paperwork in place and readily available to assist with the sale. You will need to check back on all your financials to make sure everything checks out and is properly aligned. Gather your financials, customer records, vendor contracts, sales reports, expense reports, and tax returns. Any gray areas will be examined more closely by your business broker." },
  { qLead: " ", q: "How Long Does A Business Sale Usually Take?", a: "The average timeline for completing a business sale is anywhere from six to eleven months. There are many factors in play that will affect the speed and success of the process, such as gathering the appropriate paperwork and information, reviewing the financials, and the buyer’s financing process. The purchase price, the type of business, its location and structure, among other things, will have an impact on the sale as well. Working with a professional broker will ensure that the process goes as smoothly and quickly as possible." },
  { qLead: " ", q: "How Is A Business Value Determined?", a: "Before you can sell a business, you need to know exactly how much it is worth. There are several factors that will be used to determine the value of the business. These include weighted forecasts of growth in company revenue and margin, patterns of cash returned to shareholders, changes in the company’s debt to equity ratio, and the current economic conditions of the company’s industry. Your broker will also total the assets and liabilities of the business, its current earnings, and projected earnings." },
  { qLead: " ", q: "What Are The Steps To Put A Company For Sale?", a: "When you are ready to sell your business, there are several steps that must be taken before the company can even be listed for sale. The first step is to determine the value of your company with the help of an experienced broker. You will need to clean up your finances and make sure everything is in place. Make your personal exit strategy to ensure a smooth transition, and boost your sales. Find a business broker to represent your sale, pre-qualify your buyers, and get all business contracts in order." },
  { qLead: " ", q: "Do you only advertise businesses sales locally?", a: "When you choose a broker like Phil Reese, we do everything we can to facilitate a smooth, efficient business sale without prolonging the process unnecessarily. Not only is your business advertised locally, but we will also advertise it throughout the state and even more broadly if you prefer. Sometimes, depending on the specific industry of your business, it will need to be advertised in more places than just locally in order to generate enough interested buyers." },
  { qLead: " ", q: "Which Taxes Will I Have To Pay In Order To Buy Or Sell A Business?", a: "Ultimately, the taxes you pay when selling or purchasing a business are dependent on a variety of factors. If the asset has been held for longer than 12 months, you will be required to pay long-term capital gains, which is typically 15% for most taxpayers. Any proceeds treated as ordinary income will be taxed at your individual rate. Be sure to report the business sale on your tax return through Form 4797: the sale or exchange of property." },
  { qLead: " ", q: "How Much Time Will I Have To Put Into The Business Selling Process?", a: "During the sale of a business, you can typically expect to spend about one month to negotiate offers with a buyer, a month to complete your due diligence with paperwork, financials, and contracts, and another month to close your transactions. Working with a qualified business broker will allow you to be a little more hands off during the process so you can focus on your exit strategy and continuing to manage your business successfully until the sale has completed." },
];

/* ---------- Neighborhood cards (lctn-sctn, grid-locations), verbatim ---------- */
const lctnCards = [
  { img: "lctn-01.jpg", alt: "Sell Your Company In Sun Lakes", title: "Does Your Business In Sun Lakes Need A New Owner? Contact Our Agency!", body: "Contact Phil Reese and his team for expert help selling your business and finding a new owner. We can help you plan every step of the way and prepare for a successful sale." },
  { img: "lctn-02.jpg", alt: "Sell Your Company In Provinces", title: "Want To Sell Your Company In Provinces? Give Us A Call!", body: "If you are ready to sell your company in Provinces and need guidance about how to get started or where to advertise, reach out to Phil Reese. He is licensed, experienced, and communicates well." },
  { img: "lctn-03.jpg", alt: "Sell Your Company In Cantabria", title: "Looking For Confidentiality While Selling Your Business In Cantabria? We’re Here For You!", body: "Sometimes clients want to keep the sale of a business private to ensure the least amount of impact on its success. Phil Reese is equipped to help facilitate your business sale with confidentiality, privacy, and efficiency." },
  { img: "lctn-04.jpg", alt: "Find A Business Broker For Your Company In Ocotillo Lakes", title: "Ready To Sell Your Company In Ocotillo Lakes? Call Us Today!", body: "Are you ready to sell your business, or simply have questions and don’t know where to start? Phil Reese can help! Give us a call today to discuss your questions, needs, and concerns." },
  { img: "lctn-05.jpg", alt: "Sell Your Company In Oakwood Hills", title: "Want To Buy A Business In Oakwood Hills? Contact Our Business Broker", body: "If you are ready to invest in a new business in Oakwood Hills but are having trouble gathering the appropriate paperwork or financing, contact Phil Reese and his team. We are licensed, experienced, and dedicated to helping you be successful." },
];

const IMG = "/images/chandler-business-broker";
---

<Layout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  canonical="/chandler-business-broker/"
  ogImage={ogImage}
  ogImageAlt="Chandler Business Broker | Phil Reese"
  ogImageWidth={1200}
  ogImageHeight={1200}
  structuredData={structuredData}
  videoId="75l7CluKwIg"
>
  <link slot="head" rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lite-youtube-embed@0.3.2/src/lite-yt-embed.css" />
  <script slot="head" is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lite-youtube-embed@0.3.2/src/lite-yt-embed.js" defer></script>

  <!-- 1. title-bar -->
  <section class="section title-bar">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <h1 class="maintitle h1-style">Chandler’s Leading Business Broker</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. intro (hlpr-sect) -->
  <div class="hlpr-sect">
    <h2 class="text-center">Call Phil Reese When You’re Ready To Sell Your Business In Chandler, AZ</h2>
    <div class="intro-block">
      <img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" loading="eager" src={`${IMG}/phil-portrait.jpg`} alt="Phil Reese, Chandler Business Broker" width="400" height="250" class="alignleft size-full" />
      <p>Are you looking to sell your business in Chandler? Selling your business is a big choice to make, and should be done with utmost certainty. A business sale should be done with a Certified Business Intermediary (CBI) designation, like me. You should never sell a business alone, since it’s very risky. The numerous legal concerns need good management when selling your business, and if any of them are neglected, the fees may cost more than it would have taken to hire a business broker. Selling your business with a business broker saves you money, and makes the sale easier and faster.</p>
      <p class="mb-20">I’m <a href="/about/">Phil Reese</a>, Arizona Business Broker. I have represented business owners around Arizona in selling their businesses. I am a member of the International Business Brokers Association, Past Ethics Chairman of the AZ Business Brokers Association, and one of only a few business brokers in Arizona to be designated as a Certified Business Intermediary (CBI).</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 3. test-sctn-alt — reviews title + 6 Google reviews -->
  <section class="section test-sctn test-sctn-alt">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="title-col">
        <h3 class="subtitle h3-style">Read Reviews From Our Clients</h3>
        <h4 class="h4-style">Chandler Business Broker With 5-Star Rated Reviews</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="google-col">
        <svg id="XMLID_1_" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="156.629" height="51.349" viewBox="0 0 156.629 51.349">
          <path d="M38.522,18.218H20.235v5.419H33.188c-.635,7.62-6.985,10.837-12.954,10.837A14.263,14.263,0,0,1,5.927,20.038,14.259,14.259,0,0,1,20.235,5.518a14.1,14.1,0,0,1,9.779,3.937l3.81-3.937A19.3,19.3,0,0,0,20.065.1,20.194,20.194,0,0,0,0,19.911,20.2,20.2,0,0,0,20.362,39.892c10.668,0,18.457-7.323,18.457-18.118a17.8,17.8,0,0,0-.3-3.556Z" transform="translate(0 -0.1)" fill="#4285f4"/>
          <path d="M108.769,33.6A12.806,12.806,0,1,0,121.6,46.427c.042-8.466-6.646-12.827-12.827-12.827Zm.085,5.038c3.683,0,7.2,2.963,7.2,7.789a7.381,7.381,0,0,1-7.2,7.747c-4.064,0-7.323-3.26-7.323-7.789,0-4.445,3.175-7.747,7.323-7.747Z" transform="translate(-55.303 -19.419)" fill="#ea4335"/>
          <path d="M174.969,33.6A12.806,12.806,0,1,0,187.8,46.427c0-8.466-6.689-12.827-12.827-12.827Zm.042,5.038c3.683,0,7.2,2.963,7.2,7.789a7.381,7.381,0,0,1-7.2,7.747c-4.064,0-7.323-3.26-7.323-7.789a7.4,7.4,0,0,1,7.323-7.747Z" transform="translate(-93.48 -19.419)" fill="#fbbc05"/>
          <path d="M240.676,33.6c-6.9,0-12.276,6.011-12.276,12.784a12.639,12.639,0,0,0,12.192,12.827,8.516,8.516,0,0,0,7.027-3.09v2.54c0,4.4-2.667,7.069-6.731,7.069a7.133,7.133,0,0,1-6.561-4.572l-4.911,2.074c1.736,3.683,5.249,7.535,11.514,7.535,6.858,0,12.065-4.318,12.065-13.335V34.362h-5.376v2.159a9.41,9.41,0,0,0-6.943-2.921Zm.466,5.038c3.387,0,6.858,2.879,6.858,7.789,0,5-3.471,7.747-6.9,7.747-3.683,0-7.069-2.963-7.069-7.7-.042-4.911,3.514-7.831,7.112-7.831Z" transform="translate(-131.713 -19.419)" fill="#4285f4"/>
          <path d="M326.438,33.5c-6.477,0-11.938,5.165-11.938,12.784a12.4,12.4,0,0,0,12.573,12.869,12.942,12.942,0,0,0,10.71-5.63l-4.445-2.963a7.13,7.13,0,0,1-6.265,3.514,6.57,6.57,0,0,1-6.265-3.895l17.187-7.069-.889-2.074A11.613,11.613,0,0,0,326.438,33.5Zm.254,4.953a5.082,5.082,0,0,1,4.741,2.752l-11.472,4.784c-.508-3.725,3.006-7.535,6.731-7.535Z" transform="translate(-181.365 -19.361)" fill="#ea4335"/>
          <path d="M295.2,40.86h5.63V3.1H295.2Z" transform="translate(-170.235 -1.83)" fill="#34a853"/>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <p>Over 60 reviews</p>
          <span>5.0 <span class="strs">★★★★★</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="rvw-wrapper">
        {reviews.map((r) => (
          <div class="rvw-box">
            <p>{r.body}</p>
            <div class="rvw-bx">
              <p class="name"><span class="bold"><a href={r.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">{r.name}</a></span></p>
              <span class="strs">★★★★★</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4–9 bespoke chrome wrapper -->
  <div class="hlpr-sect">
    <!-- 4. cbi-info-block -->
    <div class="grid-2-col cbi-info-block">
      <div class="col-phttxt">
        <h3>What Is A Certified Business Intermediary?</h3>
        <p>A <a href="/what-is-a-cbi/">Certified Business Intermediary (CBI) designation</a> is given by the International Business Brokers Association (IBBA) to Business Brokers who successfully complete multiple classes and tests to prove that they are competent in sales of businesses. It takes a lot of time and effort to attain the CBI designation. I had to travel around the country to attend conferences, and spend several days in mentally taxing classes on how to assist business owners in the transfer and marketing of their companies. I had to take 60 hours of classes, with a test at the end of each class to qualify for the three-hour final exam. Now, I am one of only a few Certified Business Intermediaries in Arizona.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-phtimg">
        <img decoding="async" src={`${IMG}/cbi-explainer.jpg`} alt="Chandler Business Broker Explaining What Is A Certified Business Intermediary" width="400" height="300" class="size-full" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 5. directory-flex -->
    <div class="directory-flex">
      {dirBadges.map((b) => (
        b.href ? (
          <a title={b.title} href={b.href} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img decoding="async" class="size-full" src={`${IMG}/${b.img}`} alt={b.alt} width={b.w} height={b.h} loading="lazy" />
          </a>
        ) : (
          <img decoding="async" class="size-full" src={`${IMG}/${b.img}`} alt={b.alt} width={b.w} height={b.h} loading="lazy" />
        )
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- 6. consultant-section -->
    <div class="consultant-section">
      <h3 class="tc mt-3">Top-Rated Consultant To Sell Your Business In Chandler</h3>
      <p class="mb-10">As a CBI, I’m the way to go when it comes to selling your business. I’ve helped sell over 50 businesses in Arizona, including Chandler. As a licensed real estate broker and a designated CBI, I am an expert in business sale consultations and pricings. I’m also a former business owner, so I understand what it’s like to sell your business. People sell their companies for various reasons, whether it be for family, financial reasons, or because a better opportunity has come up. Whatever the reason may be for your business sale, rest assured that I can help you with a free, professional consultation. I am affiliated with <a href="https://westusa.com/agent-roster/entry/5906/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">West USA Realty</a>, the largest business broker group in the state of Arizona. This gives your business the greatest amount of exposure possible. On top of that, more than half of my business purchasers are from outside of Arizona, and many are from outside the US. I pledge to you to be honest with you in all of our dealings, and to market your business <a href="/business-sellers/">extensively and discreetly</a>. I also pledge to negotiate your Chandler business for the best possible price, and to competently see to all of the details.</p>
      <div class="grid-2-col align-items-start mt-3">
        <div class="video-container">
          <div class="lyte-wrapper" style="width:853px;max-width:100%;margin:5px;">
            <lite-youtube videoid="75l7CluKwIg" title="Phil Reese CBI-Arizona Business Broker" style={`background-image:url('${IMG}/yt-75l7CluKwIg.jpg');`}>
              <a href="https://youtu.be/75l7CluKwIg" class="lite-yt-fallback" rel="nofollow">Watch this video on YouTube</a>
            </lite-youtube>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefits-text">
          <h4>Benefits Of Hiring A Local &amp; Experienced Business Intermediary Near You</h4>
          <p>Business owners sell their businesses for all kinds of reasons. It can be because of family, financial reasons, or because a better opportunity has come up. The best time to sell your Chandler company is when your profits and revenue have climbed. Most business owners try to sell when profits have dropped and they want out; unfortunately, by then it’s usually too late. There’s also a few things which can <a href="/business-sellers/">impede your sale</a>, such as: Trying to sell by yourself, keeping poor records, getting emotional about the sale, and pricing too high or too low. Hiring a certified business broker, like me, will increase your business’s exposure, and also make it easier to sell your company.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 7. features-grid -->
    <div class="grid-3-col features-grid mt-3">
      {features.map((f) => (
        <div class="feature-card tc">
          <img decoding="async" src={`${IMG}/${f.img}`} alt={f.alt} width={f.w} height={f.h} loading="lazy" />
